- cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems): The paper involves a team of rotorcraft working together to transport a payload, which can be considered a multi-agent system. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper may involve some AI techniques in the control and coordination of the team of rotorcraft.
